Version 2.0.0 Features Proposal
- Promisified api
- One object passed containing args and post data

API Example Usage
paystack.customer.update({
	id: 900,
	data: {
		firstname: 'Subomi',
		lastname: 'Oluwalana''
		email: 'subomi.oluwalana@yahoo.com'
		phone: 2348077886076
	}
}).then(JSON.parse)
  .then(callback);	

